<p begin='00:05:22.356' end='00:05:23.457' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>ENERGY.</span></p>
<p begin='00:05:23.490' end='00:05:26.960' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>SO IT TAKES A LOT OF ENERGY TO<br/>MAINTAIN YOUR NEUROSES AND</span></p>
<p begin='00:05:27.060' end='00:05:28.161' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>HATRED.</span></p>
<p begin='00:05:28.195' end='00:05:30.697' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>I THINK AS YOU GET OLDER YOU&apos;RE<br/>LIKE I WISH I COULD STILL BE</span></p>
